---
// CasosDisuasion.astro — Galería de disuasiones con video real
---

<section class="relative bg-hero-bg py-20 md:py-28 overflow-hidden" id="casos" role="region" aria-label="Casos de disuasión">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.025]" style="background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='32' height='32' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M0 0h32v1H0zm0 16h32v1H0z' fill='%2300ff00'/%3E%3C/svg%3E&quot;); background-repeat: repeat;"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-6 space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.7rem,3vw,2.3rem)] font-black text-white leading-tight">Así frustramos los últimos intentos de robo en la <span class="text-blue-400">Región de O'Higgins</span></h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-base max-w-2xl mx-auto">Nuestro equipo de monitoreo ha frustrado cientos de intentos de robo. Cada alerta atendida es una propiedad protegida.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 inline-block animate-pulse"></span>
        CENTRAL ACTIVA — ÚLTIMA DISUASIÓN EXITOSA: HACE 14 MINUTOS
      </span>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <article class="group bg-card-bg border border-white/5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-red-500/20 hover:-translate-y-1.5 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="relative min-h-[200px] overflow-hidden cursor-pointer video-card" data-index="0">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
          <video class="w-full h-full object-cover" muted loop playsinline preload="metadata">
            <source src="/assets/Disuasión Tepillé 04_04_2020.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          </video>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center z-20 play-overlay">
            <div class="w-[52px] h-[52px] rounded-full bg-red-600/90 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg shadow-lg animate-pulse group-hover:bg-red-700 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all play-btn">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-play ml-0.5 play-icon"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 pb-6">
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-semibold block mb-1.5">4 abril 2020</span>
          <h3 class="text-base font-extrabold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">Disuasión en propiedad residencial</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">Central detectó movimiento en perímetro. Operador activó voceo y sirena de alta potencia. Sujeto huyó antes de completar el ingreso.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 items-center">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-center gap-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot text-red-500 text-[0.65rem]"></i> Rancagua</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-center gap-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-building text-red-500 text-[0.65rem]"></i> Residencial</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-green-400 bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5">Disuasión exitosa</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="group bg-card-bg border border-white/5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-red-500/20 hover:-translate-y-1.5 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="relative min-h-[200px] overflow-hidden cursor-pointer video-card" data-index="1">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
          <video class="w-full h-full object-cover" muted loop playsinline preload="metadata">
            <source src="/assets/Disuasión Tepillé 29_03_2020.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          </video>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center z-20 play-overlay">
            <div class="w-[52px] h-[52px] rounded-full bg-red-600/90 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg shadow-lg animate-pulse group-hover:bg-red-700 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all play-btn">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-play ml-0.5 play-icon"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 pb-6">
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-semibold block mb-1.5">29 marzo 2020</span>
          <h3 class="text-base font-extrabold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">Intruso disuadido en local comercial</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">Alarma perimetral se activó por manipulación de acceso trasero. Cámaras identificaron al sujeto. Voceo inmediato logró la huida del individuo.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 items-center">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-center gap-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot text-red-500 text-[0.65rem]"></i> Machalí</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-center gap-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-store text-red-500 text-[0.65rem]"></i> Comercio</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-green-400 bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5">Disuasión exitosa</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="group bg-card-bg border border-white/5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-red-500/20 hover:-translate-y-1.5 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="relative min-h-[200px] overflow-hidden cursor-pointer video-card" data-index="2">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
          <video class="w-full h-full object-cover" muted loop playsinline preload="metadata">
            <source src="/assets/Disuasión Tepillé 10_01_2020.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          </video>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center z-20 play-overlay">
            <div class="w-[52px] h-[52px] rounded-full bg-red-600/90 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg shadow-lg animate-pulse group-hover:bg-red-700 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all play-btn">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-play ml-0.5 play-icon"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 pb-6">
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-semibold block mb-1.5">10 enero 2020</span>
          <h3 class="text-base font-extrabold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">Sospechoso disuadido en condominio</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">Operador detectó merodeo nocturno en perímetro. Se activó protocolo de voceo táctico y baliza LED. El sujeto se retiró de inmediato.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 items-center">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-center gap-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot text-red-500 text-[0.65rem]"></i> Rancagua</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 flex items-center gap-1"><i class="fa-solid fa-building text-red-500 text-[0.65rem]"></i> Condominio</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-green-400 bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5">Disuasión exitosa</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 md:gap-16 mt-12 p-8 bg-card-bg border border-white/5 rounded-xl">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="block text-[1.8rem] font-black text-red-500 leading-none">+250</span>
        <span class="block text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1.5">Disuasiones este año</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="block text-[1.8rem] font-black text-red-500 leading-none">98.7%</span>
        <span class="block text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1.5">Efectividad en disuasión</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="block text-[1.8rem] font-black text-red-500 leading-none">&lt; 45s</span>
        <span class="block text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1.5">Tiempo promedio de respuesta</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.video-card').forEach(card => {
    const video = card.querySelector('video');
    const overlay = card.querySelector('.play-overlay');
    const icon = card.querySelector('.play-icon');

    card.addEventListener('click', () => {
      if (video.paused) {
        video.play();
        overlay.classList.add('opacity-0', 'pointer-events-none');
      } else {
        video.pause();
        overlay.classList.remove('opacity-0', 'pointer-events-none');
      }
    });

    video.addEventListener('pause', () => {
      overlay.classList.remove('opacity-0', 'pointer-events-none');
    });
  });
</script>
